{"word":"G3596 - ὁδοιπορέω - hodoiporéō - hod-oy-por-eh'-o - Go on a journey","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁδοιπορέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hodoiporéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hod-oy-por-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Go on a journey</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிரயாணப்படு"},{"paragraph":"to travel, journey"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G3598 - ὁδός - hodós - hod-os'/3598\">G3598</a> and <a href=\"#/G4198 - πορεύομαι - poreúomai - por-yoo'-om-ahee/4198\">G4198</a>; to <i>be a wayfarer</i>, that is, <i>travel:</i> - go on a journey.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}